---
// zh-TW Changelog page — served at /changelog
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Changelog - ArcSign"
  description="ArcSign version history - Learn about the latest features and improvements."
  locale="zh-TW"
  canonical="https://arcsign.io/changelog"
>
  <style>
    .changelog-hero {
      padding: 120px 0 60px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #0f2b46 100%);
    }
    .changelog-hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .changelog-content {
      padding: 60px 0;
    }
    .version-item {
      margin-bottom: 48px;
      padding-bottom: 48px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }
    .version-item:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .version-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .version-number {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .version-date {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }
    .version-tag {
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .tag-latest {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2dd4bf 0%, #0d9488 100%);
      color: #fff;
    }
    .tag-beta {
      background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);
      color: #f59e0b;
      border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
    }
    .tag-release {
      background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
      color: #10b981;
      border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
    }
    .change-category {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .change-category h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .change-category h3.new {
      color: #10b981;
    }
    .change-category h3.improved {
      color: #2dd4bf;
    }
    .change-category h3.fixed {
      color: #f59e0b;
    }
    .change-category h3.security {
      color: #ef4444;
    }
    .change-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .change-list li {
      padding: 8px 0 8px 24px;
      position: relative;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .change-list li::before {
      content: "•";
      position: absolute;
      left: 8px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    }
    .back-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .back-link:hover {
      color: #fff;
    }
    .roadmap-section {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 32px;
      margin-top: 60px;
    }
    .roadmap-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .roadmap-item {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 16px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    }
    .roadmap-item:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .roadmap-status {
      width: 100px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .roadmap-status span {
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .status-planned {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    }
    .status-progress {
      background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
      color: #2dd4bf;
    }
    .status-soon {
      background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
      color: #10b981;
    }
    .roadmap-content h4 {
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .roadmap-content p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      margin: 0;
    }
  </style>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="changelog-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/" class="back-link" data-i18n="common.backHome">← 返回首頁</a>
      <h1><span class="gradient-text" data-i18n="changelog.title">更新日誌</span></h1>
      <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: 1.125rem;" data-i18n="changelog.subtitle">
        追蹤 ArcSign 的每一次進化
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Changelog Content -->
  <section class="changelog-content">
    <div class="container">

      <!-- Version 1.5.0 -->
      <div class="version-item">
        <div class="version-header">
          <span class="version-number">v1.5.0</span>
          <span class="version-tag tag-latest" data-i18n="changelog.tag.latest">最新版</span>
          <span class="version-date" data-i18n="changelog.v150.date">2026 年 6 月 23 日</span>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="new" data-i18n="changelog.cat.new">✨ 新功能</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v150.new.item1">代幣餘額免 API key — 全 7 條 EVM 鏈改走公共 RPC + Multicall3 + DefiLlama 價格，開箱即用，不再需要 Alchemy key</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v150.new.item2">Clear-signing 所見即所簽 — WalletConnect / mint 簽章在本地解碼 calldata 與 EIP-712，把 hex 變成人類可讀意圖（無上限 approve / setApprovalForAll 標紅）</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v150.new.item3">新增 Avalanche C-Chain，成為第 7 條 EVM 鏈</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v150.new.item4">手動匯入代幣 + swap 自動記錄 — 接觸過的代幣免 key 顯示餘額，清單加密存於 USB、永不離開裝置</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v150.new.item5">線上 ABI fallback（Sourcify）— 本地清單未涵蓋的已驗證合約可選擇性解碼，附一次性隱私說明與加密 USB 快取</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="fixed" data-i18n="changelog.cat.security">🔒 安全</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v150.security.item1">黑名單檢查脫離 Pro，對所有人免費 — OFAC + 惡意地址清單（go:embed 離線種子），第一次開啟、完全離線即可用</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v150.security.item2">簽章安全門移至後端 — 簽往黑名單地址時由後端在動私鑰前拒簽，除非使用者明確知情同意；前端 checkbox 僅呈現，架構上無法繞過</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v150.security.item3">所有訊息簽章路徑（EIP-191 / EIP-712）統一走 XOR 分片簽章器，無任何路徑以明文形式碰私鑰</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Version 1.2.0 -->
      <div class="version-item">
        <div class="version-header">
          <span class="version-number">v1.2.0</span>
          <span class="version-tag tag-release" data-i18n="changelog.tag.release">正式版</span>
          <span class="version-date" data-i18n="changelog.v120.date">2026 年 3 月 3 日</span>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="new" data-i18n="changelog.cat.new">✨ 新功能</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v120.new.item1">首次使用 Onboarding — 6 步驟導引流程</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v120.new.item2">OTA 自動更新 UI — 自訂更新對話框</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v120.new.item3">匿名活躍用戶追蹤 — HMAC 簽名 + IP 去重</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v120.new.item4">GA4 下載追蹤</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v120.new.item5">Windows / Linux 三平台一鍵安裝腳本</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="improved" data-i18n="changelog.cat.improved">🔧 改進</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v120.improved.item1">鏈支援精簡至 22 條</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v120.improved.item2">KyberSwap 價格影響計算修正</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v120.improved.item3">設定頁開發者模式卡片樣式統一</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="fixed" data-i18n="changelog.cat.security">🔒 安全</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v120.security.item1">修復 22 個安全漏洞</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Version 1.1.2 -->
      <div class="version-item">
        <div class="version-header">
          <span class="version-number">v1.1.2</span>
          <span class="version-tag tag-release" data-i18n="changelog.tag.release">正式版</span>
          <span class="version-date" data-i18n="changelog.v112.date">2026 年 2 月 9 日</span>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="improved" data-i18n="changelog.cat.improved">🔧 改進</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v112.improved.item1">Session Mode 文件更新 — 完善開發者模式使用說明</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v112.improved.item2">Landing Page 開發者頁面 — 新增 Session Mode 功能說明區塊</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="fixed" data-i18n="changelog.cat.fixed">🐛 修復</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v112.fixed.item1">修正 Hardhat 設定範例 — arcsign 設定應放在 network 內而非頂層</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Version 1.1.1 -->
      <div class="version-item">
        <div class="version-header">
          <span class="version-number">v1.1.1</span>
          <span class="version-tag tag-release" data-i18n="changelog.tag.release">正式版</span>
          <span class="version-date" data-i18n="changelog.v111.date">2025 年 2 月 6 日</span>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="new" data-i18n="changelog.cat.new">✨ 新功能</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v111.new.item1">交易歷史白名單過濾 — 自動過濾不在 CoinGecko 白名單內的代幣和 NFT</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="fixed" data-i18n="changelog.cat.fixed">🐛 修復</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v111.fixed.item1">RPC 多端點備援 — 解決 HTTP 429 rate limit 導致廣播失敗的問題</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Version 1.1.0 -->
      <div class="version-item">
        <div class="version-header">
          <span class="version-number">v1.1.0</span>
          <span class="version-tag tag-release" data-i18n="changelog.tag.release">正式版</span>
          <span class="version-date" data-i18n="changelog.v110.date">2025 年 2 月 6 日</span>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="new" data-i18n="changelog.cat.new">✨ 新功能</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v110.new.item1">開發者模式 — 智能合約開發者安全簽名方案</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v110.new.item2">@arcsign/hardhat-plugin — Hardhat 官方整合套件</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v110.new.item3">Block Explorer API Key 管理 — 自動注入 Etherscan、BSCScan 等 API Key</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v110.new.item4">Session 授權模式 — 測試網自動簽名，加速開發流程</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v110.new.item5">開發者簽名歷史 — 持久化儲存，支援 Block Explorer 連結</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="improved" data-i18n="changelog.cat.improved">🔧 改進</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v110.improved.item1">WebSocket 協議擴展 — 支援 EIP-191、EIP-712 簽名</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v110.improved.item2">開發者 UI — 獨立頁面設計，與一般用戶模式分離</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Version 1.0.0 -->
      <div class="version-item">
        <div class="version-header">
          <span class="version-number">v1.0.0</span>
          <span class="version-tag tag-release" data-i18n="changelog.tag.release">正式版</span>
          <span class="version-date" data-i18n="changelog.v100.date">2025 年 1 月 26 日</span>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="new" data-i18n="changelog.cat.release">🎉 正式發布</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v100.release.item1">ArcSign 正式發布 1.0.0 版本</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v100.release.item2">企業解決方案頁面 — 多簽錢包、層級授權功能預告</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v100.release.item3">版本管理機制 — 統一版本號同步工具</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="improved" data-i18n="changelog.cat.improved">🔧 改進</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v100.improved.item1">跨平台支援 (Windows、macOS、Linux)</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v100.improved.item2">優化 WalletConnect 連接穩定性</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v100.improved.item3">改進 FAQ 和使用教學文件</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Version 0.5.0 -->
      <div class="version-item">
        <div class="version-header">
          <span class="version-number">v0.5.0</span>
          <span class="version-date" data-i18n="changelog.v050.date">2025 年 1 月 23 日</span>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="new" data-i18n="changelog.cat.new">✨ 新功能</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v050.new.item1">WalletConnect v2 完整整合 — 連接 Uniswap、OpenSea 等所有支援的 dApp</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v050.new.item2">支援 eth_sendTransaction、personal_sign、eth_signTypedData_v4 簽名方法</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v050.new.item3">Session 管理介面 — 查看和管理所有 dApp 連接</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v050.new.item4">簽名狀態即時通知</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v050.new.item5">Staking 功能 — 支援 Lido、Ankr、ether.fi 等協議</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v050.new.item6">最低質押金額驗證</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="improved" data-i18n="changelog.cat.improved">🔧 改進</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v050.improved.item1">優化 Landing Page UI 設計</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v050.improved.item2">改進錢包鎖定機制 — 鎖定的錢包完全阻擋所有操作</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v050.improved.item3">調整會員錢包額度公式 (1 + NFT × 3)</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v050.improved.item4">Session token 取代 appPassword 認證方式</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="fixed" data-i18n="changelog.cat.fixed">🐛 修復</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v050.fixed.item1">修復 personal_sign 簽名驗證失敗問題</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v050.fixed.item2">修復 session recovery 無限循環</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v050.fixed.item3">修復 wallet context 持久化問題</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v050.fixed.item4">修復 estimate_fee 缺少 sessionToken 參數</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Version 0.4.0 -->
      <div class="version-item">
        <div class="version-header">
          <span class="version-number">v0.4.0</span>
          <span class="version-date" data-i18n="changelog.v040.date">2025 年 1 月 10 日</span>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="new" data-i18n="changelog.cat.new">✨ 新功能</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v040.new.item1">Pro 會員 NFT 系統 — 購買 NFT 解鎖更多錢包額度</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v040.new.item2">會員狀態頁面與購買流程</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v040.new.item3">Swap 功能優化 — 更好的價格顯示和滑點控制</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="improved" data-i18n="changelog.cat.improved">🔧 改進</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v040.improved.item1">改進交易歷史載入速度</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v040.improved.item2">優化資產餘額更新機制</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Version 0.3.0 -->
      <div class="version-item">
        <div class="version-header">
          <span class="version-number">v0.3.0</span>
          <span class="version-date" data-i18n="changelog.v030.date">2024 年 12 月 20 日</span>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="new" data-i18n="changelog.cat.new">✨ 新功能</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v030.new.item1">Token Swap 功能 — 一鍵兌換任意代幣</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v030.new.item2">詐騙代幣過濾 — 自動隱藏可疑代幣</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v030.new.item3">交易歷史記錄</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v030.new.item4">多語言支援（繁體中文、英文）</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="security" data-i18n="changelog.cat.security">🔒 安全</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v030.security.item1">實作閒置自動鎖定機制</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v030.security.item2">加強密碼輸入安全性</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Version 0.2.0 -->
      <div class="version-item">
        <div class="version-header">
          <span class="version-number">v0.2.0</span>
          <span class="version-date" data-i18n="changelog.v020.date">2024 年 12 月 1 日</span>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="new" data-i18n="changelog.cat.new">✨ 新功能</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v020.new.item1">多鏈支援 — Ethereum、BSC、Polygon、Arbitrum、Optimism、Base</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v020.new.item2">發送和接收代幣功能</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v020.new.item3">資產總覽儀表板</li>
            <li data-i18n="changelog.v020.new.item4">匯入現有錢包（助記詞）</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Version 0.1.0 -->
      <div class="version-item">
        <div class="version-header">
          <span class="version-number">v0.1.0</span>
          <span class="version-tag tag-beta" data-i18n="changelog.tag.beta">Beta</span>
          <span class="version-date" data-i18n="changelog.v010.date">2024 年 11 月 15 日</span>
        </div>
        <div class="change-category">
          <h3 class="new" data-i18n="changelog.cat.initial">✨ 初始版本</h3>
          <ul class="change-list">
